  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Thanks to its high range resolution and low hardware complexity, FMCW radar is emerging as a popular automotive radar system [90].",
    "To facilitate autonomous driving and V2X, automotive FMCW radar is expected to communicate with roadside units and nearby vehicles for real-time environment monitoring and collision avoidance, motivating research on FMCW radar-based ISAC systems [45].",
    "Nowadays, most researchers focus on effective information embedding strategies.",
    "For example, Barrenechea et al. [91] embedded the communication symbols into the FMCW waveform via AM without affecting the sensing functionality.",
    "In addition, Uysal [90] enabled the FMCW waveform to deliver the communication message in a phase-encoded manner."
  ],
